Goal : Technical section - Engineering

Please create a prototype of a "MagentAI Experience" web app.
 The prototype should represent Telekom's values, T-Systems' vision and portfolio in the field of AI & data. 
 The app should also demonstrate AI. You will briefly present this prototype in the interview, and we will discuss it. We recommend investing approximately two hours in creating the prototype. 
 The task is intentionally open-ended, be creative.

You will have approximately 10 minutes to present your "Magenta Experience" app. 